@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
[*] --> Pending
Pending --> Processing : update
Pending : entry / log driver
Processing --> Archived : update
Processing : entry / log driver
Archived --> OnHold : reject
OnHold --> Cancelled : review
Cancelled --> Closed : cancel
Cancelled : entry / log driver
Cancelled --> Closed : revert
Closed --> [*]
@enduml